Description_lang: The canister of Black Blood leaks its contents across the floor of the chamber, slowly growing in size. This pool inflicts $s1 Shadow damage and absorbs the next $s2 healing received every $t1 sec from players within the effect.Experimental Eggs that come in contact with the pool trigger a $@spellname450661.
